"                               Welcome to yubitui                               "
"                                                                                "
"Your YubiKey appears to be in factory-default state.                            "
"Here's what you can configure:                                                  "
"                                                                                "
"  [ ] Set a FIDO2 PIN — required for passkey (WebAuthn) login                   "
"  [ ] Add OATH accounts — store TOTP/HOTP codes on hardware                     "
"  [ ] Configure PIV — smart card certificates for login/VPN                     "
"  [ ] Set up OpenPGP keys — git signing, email encryption, SSH                  "
"                                                                                "
"Use the numbered keys from the dashboard to access each feature.                "
"Press ? on any screen for a protocol explanation.                               "
"  Tab  Focus   Ctrl+P  Palette   q  Quit                                        "
"                                                                                "
